message.body: Yo...you in town? When do we get to hang.
I'm in Seattle until Thursday. If you want to come up to Seattle we can hang tomorrow. Free place to stay. Family at my parents...
You should definitely come up tomorrow if you can
Ya I'm sure I can. What time are you done with everything?
Cool. Ill hit you up tomorrow
I have to cancel tonight. Have to go to a cocktail party/dinner with clients.
Sorry. Just got invited and should go since that is why I'm here. Hah
Def see you tomorrow though right?
Ya that's cool, no worries. Tomorrow for sure.
